{"tid":297364,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一直好努力改變自己命運...但係","createTime":"2017-06-25T11:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T15:08:06.000Z","uid":50076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aca6b69cf8a23f520ce95187776823fde2e4f9f6","tid":297364,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"自小家景貧窮 單親<br />\n一直好努力改變自己原本應有命運<br />\n考入大學 等緊出身<br />\n<br />\n奈何家庭問題真係比左好大壓力自己，以前以為入大學就可以解決問題，兜兜轉轉個問題冇解決仲惡化左。<br />\n<br />\n有時覺得好灰心，點解人地家庭係有助自己發展，我既家庭就係無數限制。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲一鳩樣"},{"pid":"c674d5ada8edb0b19d41ab05c8bccb9c26ba7acc","tid":297364,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"有咩難題，講黎聽下"},{"pid":"7de39663abb46bf5d51ac213a2e8a2c46f0fdbdb","tid":297364,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402628d97d5802612db7315b8e7dd78879072d74","tid":297364,"uid":30914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"你自己有咩實質目標先？"},{"pid":"61679283a5d124ebb483067c9cad06c4d6e19540","tid":297364,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"61f31b2b2abe0fffee64fea8fd971cfd5e4c78a5","tid":297364,"uid":119272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"明呀，愈大愈發覺限制太多，<br />\n總有一日會到頂點，即係包袱。<br />\n你會看破一切，明白唔係你想改變，就改變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c02ae662413083618fbbc1286dcc90404a5477f","tid":297364,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明呀，愈大愈發覺限制太多，<br />\n總有一日會到頂點，即係包袱。<br />\n你會看破一切，明白唔係你想改變，就改變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":